hedt:Pulse-artifact a hed:HedTag ;
    rdfs:label "Pulse-artifact" ;
    rdfs:comment "Example for EEG: Occurs when an EEG electrode is placed over a pulsating vessel. The pulsation can cause slow waves that may simulate EEG activity. A direct relationship exists between ECG and the pulse waves (200-300 millisecond delay after ECG equals QRS complex)." ;
